---
title: Mild Roast Veggie & Chicken Curry Pie with Brown Mustard Seeds & Filo Pastry
description: A curry pie is the blend of two perfect warm dishes coming together to deliver us a hearty dinner. Roast veggies are tossed in a mild curry sauce, with chicken and a golden filo pastry to hold all those delicious flavours together. This pie will surely be gobbled up in no time!

